% =====================================================================
% FINAL CADENCE — Bars 17-18
% Texture: Held chord; B1 grounds on F#2 (F,,); S1 descends through G#-F#
% Ends on F# major (VI of A — ecclesiastical half-verse close)
% =====================================================================
%
[V:1] G4 | F4 !eintro!|]
[V:2] (E2 D2) | C4 |]
[V:3] (C2 B,2) | A,4 |]
[V:4] (A,2 G,2) | F,4 |]
[V:5] B,4 | A4 |]
[V:6] (G2 F2) | E4 |]
[V:7] C,4 | F,,4 |]
[V:8] C,4 | F,,4 |]
